data.description: This charming house is ready to impress with its elegant features and fantastic location.The open floor plan creates a seamless flow from room to room, allowing for endless possibilities when it comes to arranging your furniture and decor. Natural light floods through the numerous windows, creating a bright and cheery ambiance throughout. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting granite countertops that provide both style and durability. The gold accent backsplash adds a touch of luxury and sophistication. You'll find stainless steel appliances that are not only sleek but also practical. After a long day, retreat to the peaceful bedrooms featuring plush carpeting for maximum comfort. The wood look tile bathroom surrounds exude elegance while being easy to maintain. And if you have a preference for low-maintenance flooring, you'll love the luxury vinyl plank flooring that extends throughout the entire home. Outside, you'll be captivated by breathtaking mountain views. Call today!
